{"pageProps":{"project":{"name":"TRIVIA!","slug":"trivia","description":"Real time Trivia app using Express + React + Socket.io + Yarn workspaces + MongoDB","stack":["react"],"content":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/LuisHCK/trivia/master/README.md","cover":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/LuisHCK/trivia/master/packages/client/public/screenshots/cover.png","links":[{"label":"View on GitHub","url":"https://github.com/LuisHCK/trivia","target":"_blank","rel":"noreferrer"},{"label":"Project details","url":"/projects/trivia"},{"label":"PlayStore","url":"https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=app.netlify.apptrivia.twa","target":"_blank","rel":"noreferrer"}]},"content":"<h1>TRIVIA!</h1>\n<p><a href=\"https://app.netlify.com/sites/apptrivia/deploys\"><img src=\"https://api.netlify.com/api/v1/badges/a4f6ad39-0d16-4185-8341-87645ad1eec5/deploy-status\" alt=\"Netlify Status\"></a></p>\n<p>Real time Trivia app using Express + React + Socket.io + Yarn workspaces + MongoDB</p>\n<h2>✨ Features</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Realtime with Socket.IO</li>\n<li>Ligthing fast React UI</li>\n<li>Authentication with Auth0</li>\n<li>Pretty fun!</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>🚀 Yarn workspaces</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://classic.yarnpkg.com/en/docs/workspaces/\">Yarn workspaces</a> is an awesome feature, it&#39;s easy to keep everything together.</p>\n<p><strong>Install NPM packages</strong></p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-bash\"># Install packages for React\nyarn workspace client add package-name\n</code></pre>\n<pre><code class=\"language-bash\"># Install packages for Express Backend\nyarn workspace server add package-name\n</code></pre>\n<h2>🏃‍♀️ How to run</h2>\n<p>Run the API server and React server with a single command</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-bash\"># With yarn\nyarn start\n</code></pre>\n<pre><code class=\"language-bash\"># With npm\nnpm run start\n</code></pre>\n<p><strong>Running server in production:</strong></p>\n<p>Install PM2</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-bash\">npm install pm2 -g\n</code></pre>\n<p>Start server daemon using included config file</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-bash\">pm2 start ecosystem.config.js\n</code></pre>\n<h2>📸 Screenshots</h2>\n<p><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/LuisHCK/trivia/master/packages/client/public/screenshots/screenshot_1.jpg\" alt=\"Trivia screenshot 1\">\n<img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/LuisHCK/trivia/master/packages/client/public/screenshots/screenshot_2.jpg\" alt=\"Trivia screenshot 2\">\n<img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/LuisHCK/trivia/master/packages/client/public/screenshots/screenshot_3.jpg\" alt=\"Trivia screenshot 3\">\n<img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/LuisHCK/trivia/master/packages/client/public/screenshots/screenshot_4.jpg\" alt=\"Trivia screenshot 4\">\n<img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/LuisHCK/trivia/master/packages/client/public/screenshots/screenshot_5.jpg\" alt=\"Trivia screenshot 5\">\n<img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/LuisHCK/trivia/master/packages/client/public/screenshots/screenshot_6.jpg\" alt=\"Trivia screenshot 7\">\n<img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/LuisHCK/trivia/master/packages/client/public/screenshots/screenshot_7.jpg\" alt=\"Trivia screenshot 7\">\n<img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/LuisHCK/trivia/master/packages/client/public/screenshots/screenshot_8.jpg\" alt=\"Trivia screenshot 8\"></p>\n"},"__N_SSG":true}